s custom plugins to connect to reset events.</p>\n<p>One example use case:  in <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://bitbucket.org/osrf/drcsim/src/9a4d632a5f3f14633b89c1012c78f8490414ff1a/plugins/ros/VRCPlugin.cc?at=vrc_plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\">drcsim's vrc plugin</a>, break pin joints if user resets model poses.</p>\n<p>Also see:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/236/race-condition-in-time-reset-for-sensors\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Race condition in time reset for sensors\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#236</s></a> - race condition in sensor update.</li>\n<li>issue <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/302/add-signal-whenever-sim-time-is-updated\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"add signal whenever sim time is updated\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#302</a> - signal when sim time advances.</li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-12-19T20:29:29.762829+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:45:16.263977+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 315}